# 2023-7442326 P-011023: Cancellation Notice

## Reference Information
* Tender reference number: PW-23-01022221
* Solicitation number: 2023-7442326 – P-011023

## Event Details
* Publication date: January 20th, 2023
* Tender closing date: March 1st, 2023 (13:00:00)
* Amendment date: February 8th, 2023
* Tender status: Canceled

## Goods and Services
The tender was originally for the provision of various professional services including program advisory services, human resource services, financial analysis services, and more.

## Trade Agreements
This tender was subject to the following trade agreements:
* Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA)
* Canada-UK Trade Continuity Agreement (Canada-UK TCA)
* Canada-Ukraine Free Trade Agreement (CUFTA)
* Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA)
* Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
* Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement
* World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO GPA)
* Atlantic Procurement Agreement
* Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)
* Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement
* Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP)
* Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA)

## Procurement Details
* Notice type: Request for Proposal
* Procurement method: Competitive - Open bidding
* Regions of opportunity: Worldwide
* Regions of delivery: National Capital Region (NCR), Ottawa, Ontario

## Contact Information
* Name: Thibault, Henri
* Email: henri.thibault@international.gc.ca
